{"id":255121,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/维权网-刘晓原律师发起为朱承志祝贺生日表达关/","date":"2012-10-06T06:01:23Z","modified":"2012-10-06T06:01:23Z","title":"维权网 | 刘晓原律师发起为朱承志祝贺生日表达关注的活动","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"more\"></a>（维权网信息员赵小明报道）湖南李旺阳离奇死亡事件被全世界关注。朱承志先生作为李旺阳的好友而亲赴邵阳调查，于<span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>遭当地警方治安拘留十天。在后又遭指控涉嫌煽动颠覆罪而被刑事拘留。其家人遭受压力，至今也没聘请律师介入。但是朱承志的遭遇一直为各界所关注，微博上要求释放朱承志的声音不绝于耳。</span>  </p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>今天（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日星期六），刘晓原律师发出呼吁，希望网民用为朱承志先生庆贺</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">62</span><span>岁生日的方式，来表达对朱承志的持续关注，从而也使朱承志家人感受到民众对他的支持，增强他们尽快采取法律行动的决心。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>刘晓原律师表示：“今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日是朱承志</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">62</span><span>周岁生日。如有网友寄贺卡，可邮送他家，地址是：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">422000</span><span>湖南省邵阳巿双清区宝东社区宝庆东路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1469</span><span>号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>栋</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>单元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">102</span><span>号。”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-7960900558003855650?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/embeddedform?hl=zh-CN&#038;formkey=dGRpN3FrVThuMFFsZHBZcmNGLW94dEE6MQ\" width=\"510\" height=\"326\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\">Loading&#8230;</iframe></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;i